<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Welcome to TiffinMitra</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0; padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Poppins', 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 70% 20%, #fffefc 0%, #f3f7fa 100%);
      background-attachment: fixed;
    }

    .wrapper {
      max-width: 480px;
      margin: 60px auto;
      border-radius: 25px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 45px rgba(100,181,246,0.22),
                  0 0 0 2px rgba(255,255,255,0.5) inset;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      overflow: hidden;
      border-top: 10px solid #6dd5fa;
      position: relative;
      animation: fadeIn 1.4s ease;
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    .floating {
      position: absolute;
      top: -35px;
      right: 25px;
      font-size: 48px;
      animation: float 3.5s ease-in-out infinite;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 3px 6px #8de2e766);
    }
    @keyframes float {
      0%,100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-10px) rotate(10deg); }
    }

    .logo-3d {
      width: 180px;
      margin: 25px auto 10px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      background: none;
      box-shadow: none;
      animation: pop 1.2s ease;
    }
    @keyframes pop {
      0% { transform: scale(0.4); opacity: 0; }
      70% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 1; }
      100% { transform: scale(1); }
    }
    .logo-3d img {
      width: 180px;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 20px;
      transition: transform 0.5s;
    }
    .logo-3d:hover img {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(270deg, #43cea2, #6dd5fa, #ffd86b);
      background-size: 400% 400%;
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 35px 20px 25px;
      border-top-left-radius: 25px;
      border-top-right-radius: 25px;
      animation: gradientMove 6s ease infinite;
      position: relative;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(67,206,162,0.3);
    }
    @keyframes gradientMove {
      0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
      50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
      100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
    }

    .header-title {
      font-size: 30px;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: 0.8px;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
    }
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #f5fbff;
      text-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }

    .divider {
      width: 80px; height: 6px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ffd86b, #79cfff);
      margin: 22px auto;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 6px #ffd86b55;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 20px 28px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content h2 {
      font-size: 22px;
      color: #263238;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .content p {
      font-size: 15.8px;
      color: #607d8b;
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .email-highlight {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #e0f7fa, #e1f5fe);
      padding: 5px 12px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      color: #00796b;
      font-weight: 700;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 6px rgba(100,181,246,0.18);
    }

    .cta-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 26px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ffe082 0%, #64b5f6 100%);
      color: #1b4b5a;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 17px;
      letter-spacing: 0.4px;
      padding: 15px 45px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      text-decoration: none;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(100,181,246,0.25);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .cta-btn:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #64b5f6 0%, #ffe082 100%);
      box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(100,181,246,0.5);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      color: #0b3c3d;
    }

    .footer {
      background: #f3f6fa;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #7b8a96;
      padding: 20px 0 12px;
      border-bottom-left-radius: 25px;
      border-bottom-right-radius: 25px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .socials img {
      width: 30px;
      margin: 0 6px;
      opacity: 0.85;
      transition: transform 0.3s, opacity 0.3s;
    }
    .socials img:hover {
      transform: scale(1.15);
      opacity: 1;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .wrapper { width: 92vw; margin: 35px auto; }
      .content { padding: 15px 20px; }
      .logo-3d img { width: 140px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="floating">🍱</div>
    <div class="logo-3d">
      <img src="tiffinmitra-logo.jpeg" alt="TiffinMitra Logo" />
    </div>

    <div class="header">
      <div class="header-title">Welcome to TiffinMitra</div>
      <div class="subtitle">Your trusted partner for homely meals 🍛</div>
      <div class="divider"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <h2>Account Created Successfully!</h2>
      <p>Hello <strong>[Your Name]</strong>,<br>
      We’re delighted to welcome you to <strong>TiffinMitra</strong> — your everyday companion for fresh, homemade, and healthy food delivered with care.</p>
      <p>Your registered email ID:</p>
      <a href="mailto:youremail@example.com" class="email-highlight">youremail@example.com</a>
      <br>
      <a href="https://tiffinmitra.example.com/login" class="cta-btn">Go to Dashboard</a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <div class="socials">
        <a href="#"><img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/733/733547.png" alt="Facebook"></a>
        <a href="#"><img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/733/733558.png" alt="Instagram"></a>
        <a href="#"><img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/733/733579.png" alt="Twitter"></a>
      </div>
      <p>© 2025 <strong>TiffinMitra</strong> | All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

